{"tid":1397520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[愛丁堡廣場內分享] 請大家相信醫護人員","createTime":"2019-08-02T13:31:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T05:14:27.000Z","uid":41701,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7fb53c2bc2fc1ddc7deca769bc6ab3c36d77dcbf","tid":1397520,"uid":41701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:31:35.000Z","msg":"好心痛地無可否認，醫護界有藍絲、有啲仲要好賤格；<br />\n但希望今日超過一萬人嘅集會可以話到俾大家知：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大部份醫護人員都係反送中架</span><br />\n<br />\n我自己係公立醫院病房護士，同時都會發夢會上前線，<br />\n有時見到一啲對醫護人員嘅批評，<br />\n好難受，<br />\n同時我真係覺得好對唔住大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但希望大家相信，我地仲有好多好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SixFjBe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSixFjBe.png&h=483eb777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n照片來源：612 reminder<br />\n<br />\n大家記得，如果不幸受傷入醫院，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔洗一定要攞身份證登記，可以無帶，可以唔見左</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">醫護人員問症一定要問，但你可以選擇唔答，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">醫生診症最重要係知道你有咩唔舒服，點解整到邊到整到其實唔重要，</span>大把獨居長者、露宿者甚至難民都會莫名奇妙咁、無人知道佢發生左咩事嘅情況下被送入病房，我地都係咁醫<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"b590bfede00f39e0ff82abca75d91569a4988815","tid":1397520,"uid":38691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:39:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bb79f5d4b2dc97d8d4e0c7705c727b7c6ab2b81","tid":1397520,"uid":38691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:40:01.000Z","msg":"公務員集會咁多人講 我地醫護都唔可以輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffeea3e990a6d9ceb5efaae31b19b22d27e0b923","tid":1397520,"uid":41701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1bb79f5d4b2dc97d8d4e0c7705c727b7c6ab2b81","tid":1397520,"uid":38691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:40:01.000Z","msg":"公務員集會咁多人講 我地醫護都唔可以輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:41:33.000Z","msg":"係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醫護人員嘅news好多都偏negative<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de6fa404dbdc2d4bd4ce401d4d49ccc53afb271","tid":1397520,"uid":288580,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:42:11.000Z","msg":"推 識好多醫護界都有發夢"},{"pid":"c49253ed6e192310e3f58f333ef088ff1eac988a","tid":1397520,"uid":38691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:51:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63f3b47849e991d6d15baab61f09e5de741ecadc","tid":1397520,"uid":296789,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:57:22.000Z","msg":"我唔敢代表其他醫護人員講d咩<br />\n但小妹90後做OPD既<br />\n除左我同另外兩位非護士職位之外<br />\n都係藍絲<br />\n之前612我請左假已經搞到一身蟻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發夢受傷之後送返去自己醫院<br />\na&amp;e同事冇咩野<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但真係好多狗</span></strong><br />\n最後都要行後門走佬<br />\n搵相熟醫生幫自己治療<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以咗多位巴絲一定要注意自己安全呀"},{"pid":"92e323e8480315d0f3a27e931d3b3691852269a3","tid":1397520,"uid":121364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b160ddd26ee02278fad6608761dcc69a50c709c7","tid":1397520,"uid":41701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63f3b47849e991d6d15baab61f09e5de741ecadc","tid":1397520,"uid":296789,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:57:22.000Z","msg":"我唔敢代表其他醫護人員講d咩<br />\n但小妹90後做OPD既<br />\n除左我同另外兩位非護士職位之外<br />\n都係藍絲<br />\n之前612我請左假