生幫自己治療<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以咗多位巴絲一定要注意自己安全呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:00:12.000Z","msg":"其實我個病房都唔少深藍或政治冷感同事，<br />\n佢地啲思維真係好難理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:03:15.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲受傷一定要求醫<br />\n但求醫都要小心！！！<br />\n我既心得係對住醫護人員都唔好講自己點受傷<br />\n時候小心留意身邊有咩人<br />\n最好盡快通知律師自己去左邊間醫院<br />\n接受治療之後要求護士唔好將個傷口包紮得太明顯/誇張<br />\n唔好拎藥果d啦盡快走人<br />\n之後出返藥房買藥都得"},{"pid":"d84d90d3a697cc33e8880207022bd638edcb7c6f","tid":1397520,"uid":176657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"我相信前線仲有好多專業既醫護人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝你地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6137c3d80f1638d9ba4583a44f7341cc6c4117","tid":1397520,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:09:36.000Z","msg":"5/8 九巴不合作運動 正式啟動！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390913</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以入group:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzaCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=dddba95e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA</a>"},{"pid":"6eb7021c065b6ab64d7de8fc3463db047374e742","tid":1397520,"uid":41701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T14:10:39.000Z","msg":"香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img